21:12.063 --> 21:13.927
TIO MARIO: [ Clears throat ]

21:13.962 --> 21:16.585
It's -- It's almost time.

21:26.008 --> 21:28.528
And I know magick
is in our blood.

21:28.563 --> 21:33.050
But that's not --
that's not everything.

21:33.084 --> 21:38.642
Love who you love and let God
figure everything else out.

21:40.816 --> 21:46.339
Listen, she will come around.

21:46.374 --> 21:48.721
I promise you.

21:48.755 --> 21:50.412
She just a little stubborn
right now.

21:50.447 --> 21:51.965
[ Chuckles ]

21:52.000 --> 21:55.106
I love you, I love you,
I love you.

21:55.141 --> 21:57.557
So proud of you.

