[ Dramatic music plays ]

22:34.076 --> 22:36.424
Your friendships are key.

22:36.458 --> 22:39.944
There's strength in your
numbers, all five of you.

22:39.979 --> 22:41.705
Work together.

22:46.157 --> 22:49.575
Mona,

22:49.609 --> 22:53.958
keep that cross on at all times.

22:53.993 --> 22:56.892
Your faith will protect you.

22:58.963 --> 23:02.070
Now, try to relax.

23:07.144 --> 23:08.732
[ Gasps ]

23:08.766 --> 23:10.250
Ohh!

23:14.116 --> 23:15.946
Did you --

23:15.980 --> 23:17.706
Did you feel that?

23:18.638 --> 23:22.711
Did you feel that?

23:22.746 --> 23:24.161
That's...

23:24.195 --> 23:26.612
[ Chuckles ]

23:26.646 --> 23:28.096
Oh, that is...

23:28.130 --> 23:31.064
oh, death magick.

23:35.517 --> 23:37.726
Mona, Mona? Is that you?

23:37.761 --> 23:39.107
Are you okay?

23:39.141 --> 23:41.730
Of course.

23:41.765 --> 23:43.491
Who else would it be?

23:43.525 --> 23:44.906
[ Breathing heavily ]

23:44.940 --> 23:47.943
That was fucking crazy.

23:47.978 --> 23:52.603
Oh, my God, don't ever
leave us like that again.

23:52.638 --> 23:55.951
New plan.

23:55.986 --> 23:57.677
Put this on ice. We'll --

23:57.712 --> 23:59.714
We'll need it later.

23:59.748 --> 24:00.991
We're not gonna finish
the ritual?

24:01.025 --> 24:03.856
No.

24:03.890 --> 24:07.100
We have a better way
of getting what we need.

24:07.135 --> 24:10.138
[ Dramatic music plays ]

24:10.172 --> 24:11.277
-Okay, wait.
-MONA: I'm good.

24:11.311 --> 24:13.210
We got you.

24:13.244 --> 24:15.661
JORDAN: Okay.

24:17.283 --> 24:19.941
Camille, you good?

24:23.703 --> 24:26.948
That was the craziest shit
I've seen in my life.

24:29.191 --> 24:31.573
I --

24:31.608 --> 24:33.920
I can't be here.

24:33.955 --> 24:35.681
Wait.

24:38.580 --> 24:41.203
When I was on the other side,

24:41.238 --> 24:43.551
I met my guides.

24:46.070 --> 24:49.798
They told me a lot of shit
I didn't understand but...

24:52.214 --> 24:57.150
Camille, they said you have
a lot of power.

24:59.221 --> 25:00.947
Dangerous power.

25:03.674 --> 25:06.643
It's basically what killed me.

25:06.677 --> 25:08.921
-The fuck?
-Me?

25:08.955 --> 25:13.339
They also said we're in danger.

25:13.373 --> 25:15.652
Of what?

25:15.686 --> 25:20.035
I don't know,
but I think somehow,

25:20.070 --> 25:23.591
bringing me back
put us all in danger.

25:23.625 --> 25:25.316
Well, maybe she's what
we're in danger of.

25:25.351 --> 25:26.939
Camille, who the fuck are you?

25:26.973 --> 25:29.769
Me?
I just met y'all tonight,

25:29.804 --> 25:31.357
and so far the only danger
I've been in is from you.

25:31.391 --> 25:34.118
It's not her.

25:34.153 --> 25:36.086
I never should have
came to Atlanta.

25:36.120 --> 25:38.019
Yes, bitch, please leave.

25:38.053 --> 25:40.815
It's not her!

25:40.849 --> 25:45.026
They told me the five of us
will have to work together

25:45.060 --> 25:46.821
to fight what's coming.

25:49.720 --> 25:54.173
It's coming for all of us.

25:58.280 --> 26:00.593
I know you are out there.

26:00.628 --> 26:03.354
Show me where you are.

26:03.389 --> 26:04.701
Come on.

26:06.081 --> 26:09.119
[ Dramatic music plays ]

26:21.856 --> 26:23.961
Really?

26:23.996 --> 26:25.791
That's how you gonna
come up in here,

26:25.825 --> 26:29.691
up in my house
after I invited you here?

26:29.726 --> 26:31.244
The disrespect.

26:31.279 --> 26:34.040
[ Groans, choking ]

26:34.075 --> 26:35.835
-Let me go!
-You know,

26:35.870 --> 26:38.286
I may not be on
The Council anymore,

26:38.320 --> 26:42.428
but my power
will always exceed your own.

26:42.462 --> 26:46.881
Now, you want to tell me why
you chose violence today?

26:46.915 --> 26:48.158
[ Coughs ]

26:48.192 --> 26:50.781
[ Breathing heavily ]

26:50.816 --> 26:53.784
I had orders on my way
into town.

26:53.819 --> 26:56.028
What kind of orders?

26:56.062 --> 26:58.237
Orders to come to Atlanta.

26:59.997 --> 27:03.449
They already thought I was here.

27:03.483 --> 27:08.040
The Council,
they detected a disruption.

27:08.074 --> 27:10.387
Powerful magick.

27:10.421 --> 27:14.322
All you had to do
was keep her away from magick.

27:14.356 --> 27:15.875
I was scrying for her

27:15.910 --> 27:18.775
until you decided to
break down my damn door.

27:18.809 --> 27:21.053
Now, come here.
I got to show you something.

27:21.087 --> 27:24.125
[ Dramatic music plays ]

27:30.200 --> 27:33.721
The pendulum landed right here.

27:33.755 --> 27:35.481
That's Mystic Haven.

27:35.515 --> 27:38.484
I think they're all
together upstairs.

27:38.518 --> 27:40.175
Well, whatever they did,

27:40.210 --> 27:43.040
it definitely got
The Council's attention.

27:43.075 --> 27:46.872
Which means it'll certainly
get Claudette's.

27:46.906 --> 27:49.944
[ Dramatic music plays ]

27:50.772 --> 27:52.222
Mm.

27:58.884 --> 28:05.028
After I harness
this death magick,

28:05.062 --> 28:07.789
I'm coming for you first!

28:22.045 --> 28:23.494
Burn.

28:23.529 --> 28:25.945
Burn!

28:34.091 --> 28:36.059
Hey.

28:36.093 --> 28:40.857
I, um, found this on the floor
while I was cleaning up.

28:43.100 --> 28:45.275
-How are you?
-[ Chuckles ]

28:45.309 --> 28:48.312
I died and came back to life,
so...

28:51.350 --> 28:53.076
A little weird.

28:56.182 --> 28:59.392
I just -- I feel different.

28:59.427 --> 29:01.118
I can't explain.

29:04.570 --> 29:05.847
No Angela?

29:05.882 --> 29:07.849
[ Chuckles ]

29:07.884 --> 29:11.542
I told her to go home
and get some rest.

29:11.577 --> 29:13.993
I just want to --
I want to be alone right now.

29:18.032 --> 29:20.310
Look,

29:20.344 --> 29:23.900
I am so happy that you're okay.

29:23.934 --> 29:25.315
God, I don't --

29:25.349 --> 29:27.938
I am so, so sorry.

29:27.973 --> 29:30.423
Look, I never meant for any of
this to happen to you, I --

29:30.458 --> 29:32.149
I know.

29:35.256 --> 29:36.982
Thank you for bringing me
back to life.

29:40.226 --> 29:43.333
I mean, did you at least
get some magick out of it?

29:43.367 --> 29:48.096
I did. But kind of used it up
in the resurrection spell.

29:52.963 --> 29:55.966
Sorry, mija.

29:56.001 --> 29:58.313
[ Sighs ]

30:00.281 --> 30:03.111
Look, I just really need
to get some rest.

30:06.149 --> 30:07.357
Right.

30:09.186 --> 30:11.326
I'll see you tomorrow.

